OL,3,C'One way or another' we're going to
OL,4,Cagree a deal with Iran, Trump tells
OL,5,CITV News
OL,7,FBy US Correspondent Dan Rivers,
OL,8,Fadditional reporting by Washington
OL,9,FNews Editor Jonathan Wald
OL,11,FAs US negotiators, led by the US Vice
OL,12,FPresident JD Vance, prepare to fly to
OL,13,FIslamabad on Tuesday for the
OL,14,Fresumption of talks with their Iranian
OL,15,Fcounterparts in Pakistan, I managed to
OL,16,Ftalk to President Trump briefly about
OL,17,Fthe chances of a deal that will
OL,18,Fformally end the war in Iran.
OL,20,FThe president sounded optimistic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
