PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776819790
OL,3,C'One way or another' we're going to
OL,4,Cagree a deal with Iran, Trump tells
OL,5,CITV News
OL,7,FHe told me: "We're gonna see... You'll
OL,8,Fknow over the next short period of
OL,9,Ftime. We're in very good shape. We'll
OL,10,Fget it one way or the other,
OL,11,Feverything is going to work out very
OL,12,Fwell. One way or the other... it makes
OL,13,Fno difference..."
OL,15,FHis upbeat assessment came just before
OL,16,Fhe is due to appear live by telephone
OL,17,Fon CNBC, the US financial channel.
OL,19,FTrump told CNBC that he thought the
OL,20,FIranians would agree to a deal with
OL,21,Fthe US because "they have no choice".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776819790
OL,3,C'One way or another' we're going to
OL,4,Cagree a deal with Iran, Trump tells
OL,5,CITV News
OL,7,F"We've taken out their navy, we've
OL,8,Ftaken out their air force, we've taken
OL,9,Fout their leaders. It is regime
OL,10,Fchange," he said.
OL,12,FMarkets have been rising in recent
OL,13,Fdays based on the expectation that a
OL,14,Flonger-term deal can be secured to
OL,15,Freopen the Strait of Hormuz, which is
OL,16,Fcurrently blockaded by both the US and
OL,17,FIran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776819790
OL,3,C'One way or another' we're going to
OL,4,Cagree a deal with Iran, Trump tells
OL,5,CITV News
OL,7,F"The market is up," Trump said. "We're
OL,8,Fgonna be at 50,000. That's where we
OL,9,Fwere just a little while ago, and when
OL,10,FI hit 50,000 on the Dow, I said,
OL,11,F'Well, I hate to do this to everybody,
OL,12,Fbut I'm gonna have to journey down to
OL,13,Fa place called Iran.' You want to see
OL,14,Fa bad stock market? Try blowing up the
OL,15,FMiddle East."
OL,17,FIn his phone call, Trump also
OL,18,Freferenced a ship bound for Iran that
OL,19,Fthe US disabled with gunfire and
OL,20,Fboarded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
