OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776819790
OL,3,C'One way or another' we're going to
OL,4,Cagree a deal with Iran, Trump tells
OL,5,CITV News
OL,7,F"We caught a ship yesterday that had
OL,8,Fsome things on it that wasn't very
OL,9,Fnice. A gift from China perhaps, I
OL,10,Fdon't know. But I was a little
OL,11,Fsurprised, because I have a very good
OL,12,Frelationship and I thought I had an
OL,13,Funderstanding with President Xi. But
OL,14,Fthat's alright. That's the way war
OL,15,Fgoes."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
