OL,3,C'One way or another' we're going to
OL,4,Cagree a deal with Iran, Trump tells
OL,5,CITV News
OL,7,FOn Monday night, the Iranians
OL,8,Fconfirmed their delegation would
OL,9,Finclude Foreign Minister Abbas Aragchi
OL,10,Fand Speaker of the Parliament Mohammed
OL,11,FBagher Ghalibath, and that they would
OL,12,Fonly attend the talks in Islamabad if
OL,13,Fthe US vice president was present.
OL,15,FThe US deadline for the current
OL,16,Fceasefire is set to expire is later
OL,17,Fthis evening US time, but White House
OL,18,Fofficials have indicated that it could
OL,19,Fbe extended if they feel they can make
OL,20,Fprogress in the Pakistan talks, due to
OL,21,Fstart on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
